Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Lupao Barangay High School in the Municipality of Lupao, Province of Nueva Ecija, to Doña Juana Chioco Barangay High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 859
An Act Changing the Name of the Lupao Barangay High School in the Municipality of Lupao, Province of Nueva Ecija, to Doña Juana Chioco Barangay High School
Section 1. The name of the Lupao Barangay High School in the Municipality of Lupao, Province of Nueva Ecija, is changed to Doña Juana Chioco Barangay High School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
